      <title>新世界集团考虑更换亿万富翁继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-adrian-cheng-as-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁郑氏家族拥有的香港房地产开发商新世界发展有限公司正考虑更换第三代继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官，此前该公司因资产减记导致 20 年来首次出现年度亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-adrian-cheng-as-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行首席财务官称其投资银行业务实现“健康”增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-investment-bank-seeing-healthy-growth-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行首席财务官詹姆斯冯莫尔特克表示，德意志银行本季度投资银行业务增长相当“健康”，交易、发起和咨询业务均比去年同期有所增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-investment-bank-seeing-healthy-growth-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Solaria 正在洽谈为房地产部门筹集 1.5 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/solaria-in-talks-to-raise-150-million-for-real-estate-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，西班牙太阳能开发商 Solaria Energia y Medio Ambiente SA 正在寻求投资者为其房地产部门注入约 1.5 亿欧元（1.68 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/solaria-in-talks-to-raise-150-million-for-real-estate-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦央行因工资下降下调通胀预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/danish-central-bank-slashes-inflation-forecasts-as-wages-cool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦央行大幅下调了今年和明年的通胀预测，暗示该北欧国家将避免出现工资-物价螺旋式上升的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/danish-central-bank-slashes-inflation-forecasts-as-wages-cool</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:08:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北方信托下调欧洲股票投资评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/northern-trust-downgrades-european-equity-exposure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northern Trust Asset Management 首席投资官 Anwiti Bahuguna 表示，该公司已下调了对欧洲股票的资产配置权重。她在彭博电视台表示：“我们刚刚对该地区持中立态度。目前情况还不足以让我们减持。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-25/northern-trust-downgrades-european-equity-exposure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:08:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行保持观望态度，裕信银行关注德国商业银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-to-stay-on-sidelines-as-unicredit-eyes-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行首席财务官詹姆斯冯毛奇（James von Moltke）周三实际上排除了目前涉足德国商业银行的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-to-stay-on-sidelines-as-unicredit-eyes-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口商担忧导致泰铢升至 2022 年 3 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国刺激计划提振了全球风险资产，泰铢升至 30 个月来的最高水平，这给泰国央行带来了采取行动抑制泰铢升值的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/baht-rises-to-strongest-since-march-2022-amid-exporters-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:27:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
