    <item>
      <title>新加坡企业向北寻求上市，马来西亚成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-takes-the-limelight-as-singapore-firms-look-north-for-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些新加坡公司正寻求在马来西亚蓬勃发展的市场上出售股票，因为这个城市国家仍将迎来二十五年来新股上市表现最糟糕的一年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-takes-the-limelight-as-singapore-firms-look-north-for-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降息预期升温，美国两年期债券收益率接近 2024 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-two-year-yields-fall-before-auction-as-rate-cut-odds-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者信心指数暴跌，短期美国国债收益率周二接近今年最低水平，这增加了美联储在下次会议上再次降息半个百分点的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-two-year-yields-fall-before-auction-as-rate-cut-odds-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
